# <type>(<scope>): <subject>
#
# <body>
#
# <footer>
#
# --- COMMIT MESSAGE TEMPLATE ---
# Type: feat (feature), fix, docs, style, refactor, test, chore, perf, ci
# Scope: Optional. Component affected (api, auth, admin, db, docker, etc.)
# Subject: Imperative mood, lowercase, no period. Max 50 chars.
#
# Body: Explain what and why, not how. Wrapped at 72 chars.
# Footer: References to issues (e.g., Fixes #123, Closes #456)
#
# --- EXAMPLES ---
# feat(auth): add JWT refresh token rotation
# fix(api): correct null pointer in rate limit filter
# docs: update database schema notes
# chore: upgrade Spring Boot to 4.0.5
